PHPLOC  
   a tool for quickly measuring the size and analyzing the structure of a PHP project.
   https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phploc
   
PHP_CodeSniffer
    a PHP5 script that tokenises and "sniffs" PHP, JavaScript and CSS files to detect violations of a defined coding standard. It is an essential development tool that ensures your code remains clean and consistent. It can also help prevent some common semantic errors made by developers
    http://pear.php.net/manual/en/package.php.php-codesniffer.intro.php
  
PHP_Depend  
    http://pdepend.org/
    PHP_Depend is a small program that performs static code analysis on a given source base
    
PHPMD
    It takes a given PHP source code base and look for several potential problems within that source
    http://phpmd.org/
    
PHPCPD
     a tool for quickly measuring the size and analyzing the structure of a PHP project
     https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phploc

phpDox
     The PHP Documentation Generator
     http://phpdox.de/getting-started.html
